Package: gargle
Title: Easier Auth for Google Services
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: c(
    person("Craig", "Citro", , "craigcitro@google.com", c("aut", "cre")),
    person("Jennifer", "Bryan", , "jenny@rstudio.com", "aut"),
    person("Google Inc", role = "cph"),
    person("RStudio", role = "cph")
    )
Description: Utilities to take some of the pain out of dealing with
    authentication and authorization for Google services and APIs. This
    includes functions and classes handling common credential types, as
    well as hooks for library authors looking to make auth easier for
    their users.
